  "prompt": "Which are the most romantic songs in Malayalam?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema has produced many romantic songs that have become timeless classics. Here are some of the most romantic songs in Malayalam:\n\n1. **\"Kanmani Anikuttan\"** - From the movie \"Narendran Makan Jayakanthan Vaka\" (2001)\n2. **\"Moham Vannu Poo Vasandhathin\"** - From the movie \"Naranathu Thampuran\" (1990)\n3. **\"Manjal Prasadavum\"** - From the movie \"Nandanam\" (2002)\n4. **\"Entammede Jimikki Kammal\"** - From the movie \"Velipadinte Pusthakam\" (2017)\n5. **\"Poomuthole\"** - From the movie \"Joseph\" (2018)\n6. **\"Sundariye\"** - From the movie \"Naranathu Thampuran\" (1990)\n7. **\"Karimizhi Kuruviye\"** - From the movie \"Kaalal Pada\" (1992)\n8. **\"Aaro Nenjil\"** - From the movie \"Kakkakuyil\" (2001)\n9. **\"Chinna Chinna Aasai\"** - From the movie \"Sukhrutham\" (1994)\n10. **\"Mazhavil Kavadiyil\"** - From the movie \"Neelakkuyil\" (1954)\n\nThese songs often feature beautiful melodies and poignant lyrics, expressing love and romance in various forms. They are cherished by fans of Malayalam music and cinema.",
